---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Garis Waktu Naratif - The Soulforge Saga">
  <div class="w-full max-w-6xl glass-card p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-border-color flex flex-col h-[95vh]">
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-white tracking-wider mb-6 text-center drop-shadow-lg" data-i18n-key="narrative_timeline_title">
      Garis Waktu Naratif
    </h1>

    <div class="flex-grow flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-6 overflow-hidden">
      <!-- Timeline Visualization -->
      <div class="flex-grow bg-slate-800/60 rounded-xl p-4 overflow-auto scrollbar-thin">
        <div id="timeline-container" class="relative h-full min-h-[500px]">
          <!-- Timeline visualization will be rendered here -->
          <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-0 right-0 h-1 bg-indigo-500 transform -translate-y-1/2"></div>
          
          <!-- Sample timeline events -->
          <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/4 transform -translate-y-1/2 -translate-x-1/2">
            <div class="w-4 h-4 bg-indigo-500 rounded-full border-2 border-white"></div>
            <div class="mt-2 w-48 glass-card p-3 rounded-lg">
              <h3 class="font-bold text-white">Awal Mula</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-300">Penciptaan dunia pertama</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 transform -translate-y-1/2 -translate-x-1/2">
            <div class="w-4 h-4 bg-indigo-500 rounded-full border-2 border-white"></div>
            <div class="mt-2 w-48 glass-card p-3 rounded-lg">
              <h3 class="font-bold text-white">Kebangkitan</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-300">Munculnya peradaban pertama</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-3/4 transform -translate-y-1/2 -translate-x-1/2">
            <div class="w-4 h-4 bg-indigo-500 rounded-full border-2 border-white"></div>
            <div class="mt-2 w-48 glass-card p-3 rounded-lg">
              <h3 class="font-bold text-white">Konflik</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-300">Perang antar kerajaan</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Event Details Panel -->
      <div class="flex-shrink-0 bg-slate-800/60 rounded-xl p-4 lg:w-80 flex flex-col space-y-4 overflow-y-auto scrollbar-thin">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2" data-i18n-key="event_details_title">Detail Peristiwa</h3>
        
        <div id="event-details" class="space-y-3">
          <div class="glass-card p-4 rounded-lg">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-white">Awal Mula</h4>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-300 mt-2">Pada awal zaman, para Forger menciptakan dunia pertama dengan kekuatan pikiran mereka. Energi primordial mengalir melalui urat-urat realitas, membentuk daratan, lautan, dan langit.</p>
            <div class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-indigo-600 text-xs rounded">Penciptaan</span>
              <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-green-600 text-xs rounded">Awal Zaman</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="mt-4">
            <label class="block text-slate-400 text-sm mb-1" data-i18n-key="event_title_label">Judul Peristiwa</label>
            <input type="text" class="glass-input w-full p-2" placeholder="Masukkan judul peristiwa">
          </div>
          
          <div>
            <label class="block text-slate-400 text-sm mb-1" data-i18n-key="event_description_label">Deskripsi</label>
            <textarea class="glass-input w-full p-2 h-24" placeholder="Masukkan deskripsi peristiwa"></textarea>
          </div>
          
          <div>
            <label class="block text-slate-400 text-sm mb-1" data-i18n-key="event_tags_label">Tag</label>
            <input type="text" class="glass-input w-full p-2" placeholder="Tag (dipisahkan koma)">
          </div>
          
          <button id="add-event-btn" class="glass-button primary-button w-full mt-2">
            <i data-lucide="plus"></i> <span data-i18n-key="add_event">Tambah Peristiwa</span>
          </button>
          
          <button id="save-timeline-btn" class="glass-button secondary-button w-full mt-2">
            <i data-lucide="save"></i> <span data-i18n-key="save_timeline">Simpan Garis Waktu</span>
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <button id="back-to-forger-btn" class="glass-button secondary-button mt-8">
      <i data-lucide="arrow-left" class="w-5 h-5 mr-2"></i> <span data-i18n-key="back_to_forger_dashboard">Kembali ke Dashboard Forger</span>
    </button>
  </div>
</MainLayout>